{"id":266896,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-成都访民维权「简报」第二十五期/","date":"2012-12-05T17:15:54Z","modified":"2012-12-05T17:15:54Z","title":"维权网 | 成都访民维权「简报」第二十五期","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012-11-15</span><span>＿＿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11-30</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>宗旨：给政府提供维稳线索；留下访民辛酸足迹（冰山一角）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，成都锦江强拆访民李廷惠被成都锦江公安分局行政拘留满</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天后，警方还准备刑事拘留她，劳教她，安靖看守所体检后，说她有病不接受，被释放回家，监视居住。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊强拆访民岳中顺、岳中芳到市政府信访办上访，由市委秘书长黄大超接待。接待完，他安抚说，你们回去，他们会给你解决的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区东坡办事处李全玉、李华峻、陈秀容、孙玉等十多人到市政府上访，由市委秘书长黄大超接待。但访民晚上回家受到马兴国安排的黑社会人员威胁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、金牛区强拆访民严塔凤进京上访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>在前门被截访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日被送回成都。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、双流强拆访民周文明、杨芳、李志安进京上访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>在前门被截访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日被送回成都。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊草堂办事处邓晓瑛在十八大敏感时期又一次从北京截访回来，可是她的行李却没能带走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11?8</span><span>被截访</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>号送回，然后送蒲江农家乐黑监狱，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>，锦江成龙办事处彭</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">xx</span><span>在十八大敏感时期又一次从北京截访回来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日锦江双桂街办刘辉涛被截访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>号送简阳龙泉湖桃花岛黑监狱，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>号释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>个人看守。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>、金牛区强拆访民陈茜也是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日被截访回来，严加看守，不准出门，由看守的人给她买菜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，廖才俐被旅游回家。据悉她是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>被带走旅游。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>、锦江区强拆访民袁雪梅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>号进京上访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>号被截访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>送回成都，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>晚上回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>带到一农家乐关黑监狱，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>被释放回家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，锦江区强拆访民李廷惠向成都市公安局申请成都市公安局锦江公安分局对她的行政拘留行政复议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，强拆访民周成群向成都市公安局申请成都市公安局锦江公安分局对她的行政拘留行政复议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>号，青羊文家何艾芩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>从北京被骗截访回关在家中，不让外出。今日，政府派看守对她施暴，不让吃饭。报警，警察来后，政府看守人员将她反锁在家，警察见门锁闭也没做搭救，扬长而去。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，锦江区强拆访民李廷惠电话李发清，她回答，她被监控在家，不得外出。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，金牛强拆访民陈茜、林龙华夫妇被解除看守。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区苏坡办事处强拆访民彭燕，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>被截访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日被送回成都拉到蒲江农家乐黑监狱，被看守到今天才释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>青羊文家失地农民李华成得到成都市公安局通知，让他去拿被行拘申请复议的答复。他去后，警官说是口头答复，在他坚持下，警察答应下午再来，等下午去，另一警察说仍口头答复，若坚持要书面等段时间再说。李华成说，警方如错了，你们连面对错误的勇气都没有了吗？还奢谈纠正？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区文家乡访民何艾芩逃脱监控，进城向朋友们求助。据悉她</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>上访被截访回一直被反锁看守在家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区东坡办事处岳中顺、岳中芳、李全玉到市政府信访办上访，接待人员只着了简单登记，无任何说法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊文家何艾芩到青羊区文家派出所报案：她</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日被政府看守施暴。警察不做笔录。在她向督察投诉后，警方才记录案情。但警方威胁她，做的笔录和证据我们随时可以销毁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊文家何艾芩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日受当地警察威胁，她不放心，到成都市公安局督察投诉，督察做了详细记录。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区广华办事处强拆访民董春模，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>号被截访回便拉到蒲江县一农家乐关黑监狱，今天被释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区金沙街办刘存钦被关</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>天黑监狱后释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>进京上访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>在国土资源部被截访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日被送蒲江一黑监狱，到地方后，街道办维稳杨书记就拼命地给刘存钦一耳光，将她打得旋转一二圈几乎晕死过去。杨还摆上绳索木棒命令打手扬言：随便打，打死了他负责，是上面安排打的。看你还告不告。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，周成群、李廷惠、陈伦珍到成都市中级人民法院，反映中级人民法院立案受理了的行政赔偿诉讼案违法移交到基层法院审理。基层法院和中级人民法院都在打太极至今压案不审理，法院依法不許可代理人给我们代理等问题。接待人赖法官。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>随后，她们又到中级人民法院立案庭反映，原告周成群、易萍、刘菊琴等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>人诉被告成都市锦江区人民政府行政赔偿一案，这个集体案是成都中级人民法院郑惠法官经办的，周成群又打电话（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">82915468</span><span>）联系了郑惠法官，反映这个集体案的重要问题，郑惠称：‘’所有的行政赔偿案都是法院内部规定移交到基层法院申理。‘’还没有等周成群反应问题，郑法官很快挂了电话。周成群又打几次电话就再也没人接电话了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，崇州江源镇玉成园艺种植场陈敏的苗木遭到政府挑动来的村民的毁坏。原因是合同没到期，政府想毁约故指使当地村民倒腾所致。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊草堂办事处强拆访民邓晓英到街道办事处，询问她</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>号被黑保安抢走又交给政府办工作人员的电话卡、截访时被拉下的物品的下落，以及她被关</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>天黑监狱的说法和从黑监狱出来时答应的一周之内开她问题解决的协调会。街道办书记不在，由副主任接待，但他说，他做不了结主，他只能给领导反映。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊文家何艾芩到成都市公安局督察询问自己的反映问题的解决情况，督察答复，他们已安排调查，叫她在家等结果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区东坡杨邦惠按政府约定到街道办事处核实一下她反映的问题。反复核实后，街道办张副书记说，政府打算不按以前的产权交换协议执行，仍坚持过去的已执行的货币执换。但政府拿不出后者的协议书。政府见说服不了她，就让她等他向领导反映后再说。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区文家何艾芩到省纪委、省政府及组织部上访，省纪委只做了登记没做回答。省政府没登记，联系青羊区政府接待，等她赶到区政府，政府不但不接待，接待领导还辱骂她。随后到组织部，组织部推萎她到区上解决问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，成都市访民周成群、李廷惠到成都锦江区公安分局反映</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>个问题。一是周成群、李廷惠被锦江区公安局行政处</span><span></span><span>罚拘留没给二人原件拘留处罚决定书，，法制办警官（警号为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">005769</span><span>）称不是我们送你们去拘留的，是成龙派出所送你们去拘留的。他还称：</span><span> </span><span>“你们没有原件，怎会被拘留？你们的复印件又是哪里来的？”周成群回答：“拘留复印件是锦江公安分局邮政方式寄来的。”警号为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">005679 </span><span>的警官称：“我调查清楚再通知你们。”二是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>公安局长进大厅活动，周成群、李廷惠、陈伦珍到公安局长进大厅活动现场反映问题，在大厅门口被成龙派出所副所长陈建</span><span> </span><span>明等人强制拉上警车送到了成龙办事处控制限制人生自由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>三人向锦江分局交了公安行政赔偿申请书，已三个月没有给书面答复，今天法制</span><span> </span><span>办</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">005769</span><span>号的警官拿出三人的不予受理通知书叫三人签收，而且警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">005769</span><span>的警官称：“你们签名，我填日期。”这个警官耍花招，他填的日</span><span> </span><span>期为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>。我们说：“今天签收就应该填今天的日子。”他来的霸道称：“你们要不要，不要就算了。”今天的两个问题是他都是胡作非为；三人报了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>警官（警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">007181</span><span>）出警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">32</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>，成都市锦江区访民周成</span><span> </span><span>群、李廷惠到锦江区成龙派出所找刑警队长董承健（</span><span> </span><span>警号为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">006558</span><span>）讨要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月日被送进拘留所的原件行政处</span><span> </span><span>罚决定书。董承健称：“不是我送你们去的，去找送你</span><span> </span><span>们去的要。”当时送周成群、李廷惠进拘留所时，经办人是治安民警</span><span> </span><span>高绍军</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>警号为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">006237)</span><span>警官。周、李又找到高警官，高</span><span> </span><span>警官称：“去找分局。”态度极其恶劣。周成</span><span> </span><span>群、李廷惠被锦江区成龙派出所的警官赶出了门，也没</span><span> </span><span>有得到拘留证的原件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">33</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，成都市金堂淮口同兴社区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>组冤民杨世合到市政府、省政府上访，都拒绝接待。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>「遗漏补充」：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、草市街辖区的文殊院访民蒋秀蓉因为多年多次上访都没有得到她的六年营业损失，十八大期间</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日到北京上访，没有注意一直有人跟踪，结果到了北京西站下车后，被当地政府截访，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>回到成都。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>「更正」：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、上期第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>条“…孙玉、李俊、李发俊、李泉玉…”更为“…孙玉、李俊、李泉玉…”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1006122108976190954?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.co